# field


Create a field of arrows and let this field run through a evolution. The idea:

1. Choose one random arrow of the field.
2. Take a look at which neighbor this arrow is pointing.
   This one will be next arrow which will be forced to rotate in a random direction.
3. rotate the arrow
4. Continue with step 2 ...



+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+
|  |  |     |  ^  |     |  |  |     |  |  |     |
|  |  | <-- |  |  | --> |  |  | <-- |  |  | <-- |
|  v  |     |  |  |     |  v  |     |  v  |     |
+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+
