+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+-----+



Version 2

  <  <  <  <
  >  >  >  >
  v  v  v  v
  n  n	n  n

Version 2

  <  <  <  <
  >  >  >  >
  V  V  V  V
  A  A	A  A

  Version 3

  2  2  2  2   down
  1  1  1  1   right
  3  3  3  3   left
  0  0	0  0   up
